ge your Adoption Leave start date if you give your employer at least 28 days’ notice - you can change the end date if you give 8 weeks’ notice.</p>\n</div>\n"}]},"updated_at":"2012-10-22T15:25:03+00:00","tags":[{"title":"Holidays, time off, sick leave, maternity and paternity leave","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/working%2Ftime-off.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes career breaks and the holiday entitlement calculator","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=working%2Ftime-off","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/working/time-off"},"parent":{"title":"Working, jobs and pensions","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/working.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes holidays and finding a job","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=working","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/working"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Having a child and adoption","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/births-deaths-marriages%2Fchild-adoption.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Legal rights, birth certificates, parental rights and child maintenance","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=births-deaths-marriages%2Fchild-adoption","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/births-deaths-marriages/child-adoption"},"parent":{"title":"Births, deaths, marriages and care","id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/tags/births-deaths-marriages.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes civil partnerships and lasting power of attorney","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/with_tag.json?tag=births-deaths-marriages","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/births-deaths-marriages"},"parent":null}}],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/paternityleave.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/paternityleave","title":"Paternity Leave","format":"programme","details":{"need_id":"1759","business_proposition":false,"d